&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle from qualification through close for SMB, startup, AI-native, and enterprise customers — including well-known global brands entering generative AI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage a book of 30-50+ accounts, driving retention, adoption, and expansion — turn initial use cases into broader adoption across teams, products, and business units&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify inbound leads and run outbound prospecting into target segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute sales campaigns in collaboration with sales leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle deals across API access and weight licensing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate customer needs and usage patterns into expansion opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with solutions engineering and product on technical questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ve closed real deals, you move fast, and you&#39;re hungry to have outsized impact at a company where your work directly drives revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
