&lt;li&gt;Track record of managing a high volume of accounts and deals in parallel without dropping balls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong outbound instincts — can build pipeline, not just work inbound&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in a startup, scale-up, or high-growth environment where process didn&#39;t exist yet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized, disciplined, and self-directed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bonus: background in generative AI, image/video generation, or open-source business models&lt;/li&gt;
