&lt;li&gt;Distributed systems experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Slurm and Kubernetes for job orchestration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with object storage performance tuning across providers&lt;/li&gt;
